properties.areaDesc: Coastal Palm Beach County; Metro Palm Beach County; Inland Palm Beach County
properties.headline: Special Weather Statement issued February 14 at 7:38PM EST by NWS Miami FL
properties.description:
* At 737 PM EST, National Weather Service meteorologists were
tracking a strong shower near Boynton Beach, moving southeast at 5
mph.

* Funnel clouds possible with this shower.

* Locations impacted include...
Boca Raton, Boynton Beach, Delray Beach, Highland Beach, Ocean
Ridge, Lantana, Village Of Golf, Kings Point, Whisper Walk,
Hamptons At Boca Raton, Hypoluxo, Gulf Stream, Briny Breezes,
Manalapan, Aberdeen, Aberdeen Golf Course, Morikami Park, Villages
Of Oriole and Boca Raton Equestrian.
properties.instruction:
This activity was also developing in an environment favorable for the
formation of funnel clouds. Stay tuned to NOAA weather radio and
local media for additional updates and possible warnings.

To report severe weather, contact your nearest law enforcement
agency. You can also share your report with NWS Miami on Facebook and
Twitter.

NWSheadline: SIGNIFICANT WEATHER ADVISORY FOR SOUTHEASTERN PALM BEACH COUNTY UNTIL 815 PM EST
